value.0: This bed has a beaten straw mattress, lined with well worn cotton sheets and covered with a worn woolen blanket.  Tended quite well, washed and scented, you will not find any bedbugs living here.  Soft enough to allow even the most hard adventurer a decent nights rest.

This was a lime in water, which most considered to be rather refreshing on hot days.
